article_node.title: Best Google Pixel 9 and Pixel 9 Pro plans in Australia (August 2025)
article_node.summary: Google recently announced the Pixel 10 series, which includes the Pixel 10, Pixel 10 Pro, Pixel 10 Pro XL, and Pixel 10 Pro Fold, with preorders now available. The new models feature the Tensor G5 chipset, improved camera capabilities including a telephoto lens, and enhanced AI features. The Pixel 9 series remains a strong contender in the market, offering excellent value and performance, especially as prices are expected to drop with the release of the new models.
